{
  "stem": "6777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went out by car with the engineers to the building site.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The engineers in-- stayed in the building site.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have been there, too, and gave the workers some money or whatever-- official.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I disappeared [LAUGHS] and came back much later by myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my Polish resistance friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the male friends of mine, they have been going to all sort of exercises, Home Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because I've been Jewish, they feared that I might be give-- giving away things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I have been assigned, because of the good knowledge of German, to report all sort of things like movements of trains and this sort of things-- movements of supplies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, there have been other people who also planned and had friends on the other side and wanted to smuggle out some money or things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, I had, in my back teeth, the biggest molars-- drilled out and put on just cheap, little crowns, not gold ones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And underneath, I smuggled diamonds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or in winter, in the very end of the glove, I smuggled [LAUGHS] rings and other things out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I brought the Kennkarten, the Polish-- for the-- when somebody wanted to go onto the Polish side and ask for false paper--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the Germans came, after the siege of Warsaw, they have ordered a-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you register everybody-- what is it called, for goodness sake?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every four years, you have it here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A census.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Now, they ordered a census but with it, also, the issuing of cards, of identity cards.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Kennkarte is really, in English, an identity card with a photograph and with--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stamp, finger--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fingerprint.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
